856]},{"content":"Use the POS to look up available inventory in WHS-enabled stores.","pos":[74409,74474]},{"content":"When you look up inventory, the process should work the same as it worked before.","pos":[74497,74578]},{"content":"The lookup should show the available quantities at the warehouse level, and should not consider the Location, Inventory status, or License plate dimensions.","pos":[74579,74735]},{"content":"Use the POS to process a product receipt for a transfer order in a WHS-enabled store.","pos":[74740,74825]},{"content":"You can receive transfer orders at the POS for a WHS-enabled store and items.","pos":[74828,74905]},{"content":"The user should be able to select the locations to receive into, and should be able to enter license plate IDs to automatically populate the receiving lines.","pos":[74906,75063]},{"content":"Use the POS to process a product receipt for a purchase order in a WHS-enabled store.","pos":[75071,75156]},{"content":"You can receive purchase orders at the POS for a WHS-enabled store and items.","pos":[75159,75236]},{"content":"The user should be able to select the locations to receive into, and should be able to enter license plate IDs to automatically populate the receiving lines.","pos":[75237,75394]},{"content":"Use the POS to process a shipment of products from a WHS-enabled store.","pos":[75402,75473]},{"content":"You can register transfers from the POS for a WHS-enabled store and items.","pos":[75490,75564]},{"content":"The user should be able to select the locations to ship from, the inventory status should be automatically generated, and license plates should be ignored.","pos":[75565,75720]},{"pos":[75736,75773],"content":"Enable seamless omni-channel commerce","linkify":"Enable seamless omni-channel commerce","nodes":[{"content":"Enable seamless omni-channel commerce","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Seamless omni-channel commerce refers to management and order processing across brick-and-mortar stores, online storefronts, 